title: George Santos Says He Expects to Be Kicked Out of Congress as Expulsion Vote Looms
description: Rep. George Santos has said he expects to be expelled from Congress following a scathing report by the House Ethics Committee.

title: Ukraine’s Military Says Russia Launched Its Largest Drone Attack Since the Invasion
description: Russia launched its most intense drone attack on Ukraine since the beginning of its full-scale invasion in 2022, military officials said.

title: Killing of Female Student Sparks Mass Protests in Italian Cities
description: Thousands of protesters took to the streets of Italy’s biggest cities to voice outrage at violence against women.

title: Derek Chauvin Has Reportedly Been Stabbed in Federal Prison. Here’s What to Know
description: Derek Chauvin, a former police officer convicted of murdering George Floyd, was reportedly stabbed in prison.

title: Victims in Niagara Falls Border Bridge Crash Identified as Western New York Couple
description: The two people killed when their car crashed into a border checkpoint in Niagara Falls were identified as a New York husband and wife.
